# game/indepth_transitions.rpy:56
translate indonesian demo_transitions_5bbc72fe:

    # e "Ren'Py ships with a large number of built-in transitions, and also includes classes that let you define your own."
    e "Ren'Py hadir dengan banyak sekali transisi bawaan, dan juga menyertakan kelas-kelas yang memungkinkan kamu menentukan transisi kamu sendiri."

# game/indepth_transitions.rpy:60
translate indonesian demo_transitions_menu_3caf78d3:

    # e "What kind of transitions would you like demonstrated?"
    e "Jenis transisi apa yang ingin kamu lihat demonstrasinya?" 
# game/indepth_transitions.rpy:95
translate indonesian demo_simple_transitions_2b4fbae3:

    # e "Okay, I can tell you about simple transitions. We call them simple because they don't take much in the way of configuration."
    e "Oke, saya bisa memberitahu kamu tentang transisi sederhana. Kami menyebutnya sederhana karena tidak memerlukan banyak konfigurasi." 
# game/indepth_transitions.rpy:97
translate indonesian demo_simple_transitions_4b235ac2:

    # e "But don't let that get you down, since they're the transitions you'll probably use the most in a game."
    e "Tapi jangan biarkan hal itu membuat kamu kecewa, karena itu adalah transisi yang kemungkinan besar akan paling sering kamu gunakan dalam sebuah game." 
# game/indepth_transitions.rpy:103
translate indonesian demo_simple_transitions_af0431ac:

    # e "The 'dissolve' transition is probably the most useful, blending one scene into another."
    e "Transisi 'dissolve' mungkin yang paling berguna, membaurkan satu adegan ke adegan lainnya." 
# game/indepth_transitions.rpy:109
translate indonesian demo_simple_transitions_5b9f711f:

    # e "The 'Dissolve' function lets you create your own dissolves, taking a different amount of time."
    e "Fungsi 'Dissolve' memungkinkan kamu membuat dissolve sendiri, dengan durasi waktu yang berbeda." 
# game/indepth_transitions.rpy:116
translate indonesian demo_simple_transitions_79816523:

    # e "The 'fade' transition fades to black, and then fades back in to the new scene."
    e "Transisi 'fade' memudar ke hitam, lalu memudar kembali ke adegan baru." 
# game/indepth_transitions.rpy:118
translate indonesian demo_simple_transitions_141bb95d:

    # e "If you're going to stay at a black screen, you'll probably want to use 'dissolve' rather than 'fade'."
    e "Jika kamu akan tetap berada di layar hitam, kamu mungkin ingin menggunakan 'dissolve' daripada 'fade'." 
# game/indepth_transitions.rpy:123
translate indonesian demo_simple_transitions_f059f4ae:

    # e "You can use 'Fade' to define your own fades. By changing the timing and the color faded to, you can use this for special effects, like flashbulbs."
    e "Kamu dapat menggunakan 'Fade' untuk menentukan fade kamu sendiri. Dengan mengubah waktu dan warna tujuannya, kamu dapat menggunakan ini untuk efek khusus, seperti lampu kilat kamera." 

# game/indepth_transitions.rpy:129
translate indonesian demo_simple_transitions_e948905b:

    # e "The 'pixellate' transition pixellates out the old scene, switches to the new scene, and then unpixellates that."
    e "Transisi 'pixellate' mempikselkan adegan lama, beralih ke adegan baru, lalu menghilangkan pikselnya." 

# game/indepth_transitions.rpy:131
translate indonesian demo_simple_transitions_6a1ae05f:

    # e "It's probably not appropriate for most games, but we think it's kind of neat."
    e "Ini mungkin tidak cocok untuk sebagian besar game, tetapi menurut kami ini cukup unik." 

# game/indepth_transitions.rpy:134
translate indonesian demo_simple_transitions_bdfcd85a:

    # e "You can use 'Pixellate' to change the details of the pixellation."
    e "Kamu dapat menggunakan 'Pixellate' untuk mengubah rincian pikselasinya." 

# game/indepth_transitions.rpy:136
translate indonesian demo_simple_transitions_432f7224:

    # e "Motions can also be used as transitions."
    e "Gerakan juga dapat digunakan sebagai transisi." 

# game/indepth_transitions.rpy:146
translate indonesian demo_simple_transitions_fbf11906:

    # e "Hey! Pay attention."
    e "Hei! Perhatikan." 

# game/indepth_transitions.rpy:148
translate indonesian demo_simple_transitions_51c1c5b8:

    # e "I was about to demonstrate 'vpunch'... well, I guess I just did."
    e "Tadinya saya ingin mendemonstrasikan 'vpunch'... yah, sepertinya baru saja saya lakukan." 

# game/indepth_transitions.rpy:154
translate indonesian demo_simple_transitions_57f19473:

    # e "We can also shake the screen horizontally, with 'hpunch'. These were defined using the 'Move' function."
    e "Kita juga bisa mengguncang layar secara horizontal dengan 'hpunch'. Ini ditentukan menggunakan fungsi 'Move'." 

# game/indepth_transitions.rpy:156
translate indonesian demo_simple_transitions_fce83e12:

    # e "There's also the 'move' transition, which is confusingly enough defined using the 'MoveTransition' function."
    e "Ada juga transisi 'move', yang cukup membingungkan karena ditentukan menggunakan fungsi 'MoveTransition'." 

# game/indepth_transitions.rpy:164
translate indonesian demo_simple_transitions_1050b6a4:

    # e "The 'move' transition finds images that have changed placement, and slides them to their new place. It's an easy way to get motion in your game."
    e "Transisi 'move' menemukan gambar yang posisinya berubah, lalu menggesernya ke tempat baru. Ini adalah cara mudah untuk mendapatkan gerakan di dalam game kamu." 

# game/indepth_transitions.rpy:168
translate indonesian demo_simple_transitions_dc776e59:

    # e "That's it for the simple transitions."
    e "Itu saja untuk transisi sederhana."

# game/indepth_transitions.rpy:175
translate indonesian demo_imagedissolve_transitions_2db67018:

    # e "Perhaps the most flexible kind of transition is the ImageDissolve, which lets you use an image to control a dissolve."
    e "Mungkin jenis transisi yang paling fleksibel adalah ImageDissolve, yang memungkinkan kamu menggunakan gambar untuk mengontrol dissolve." 

# game/indepth_transitions.rpy:177
translate indonesian demo_imagedissolve_transitions_429f8d03:

    # e "This lets us specify very complex transitions, fairly simply. Let's try some, and then I'll show you how they work."
    e "Ini memungkinkan kita menentukan transisi yang sangat kompleks dengan cukup sederhana. Mari kita coba beberapa, lalu saya akan tunjukkan cara kerjanya." 

# game/indepth_transitions.rpy:179
translate indonesian demo_imagedissolve_transitions_1ce501b0:

    # e "There are two ImageDissolve transitions built into Ren'Py."
    e "Ada dua transisi ImageDissolve yang sudah terpasang di Ren'Py." 

# game/indepth_transitions.rpy:191
translate indonesian demo_imagedissolve_transitions_ea0413be:

    # e "The 'blinds' transition opens and closes what looks like vertical blinds."
    e "Transisi 'blinds' membuka dan menutup sesuatu yang terlihat seperti tirai vertikal." 

# game/indepth_transitions.rpy:201
translate indonesian demo_imagedissolve_transitions_12e2e0d0:

    # e "The 'squares' transition uses these squares to show things."
    e "Transisi 'squares' menggunakan kotak-kotak ini untuk menunjukkan berbagai hal." 

# game/indepth_transitions.rpy:203
translate indonesian demo_imagedissolve_transitions_bbf73d1c:

    # e "I'm not sure why anyone would want to use it, but it was used in some translated games, so we added it."
    e "Saya tidak yakin mengapa ada orang yang ingin menggunakannya, tetapi transisi ini digunakan dalam beberapa game terjemahan, jadi kami menambahkannya." 

# game/indepth_transitions.rpy:207
translate indonesian demo_imagedissolve_transitions_0ab2902d:

    # e "The most interesting transitions aren't in the standard library."
    e "Transisi yang paling menarik tidak ada di pustaka standar." 

# game/indepth_transitions.rpy:209
translate indonesian demo_imagedissolve_transitions_54aa9bf9:

    # e "These ones require an image the size of the screen, and so we couldn't include them as the size of the screen can change from game to game."
    e "Transisi ini memerlukan gambar seukuran layar, jadi kami tidak bisa menyertakannya karena ukuran layar dapat berubah-ubah di setiap game." 

# game/indepth_transitions.rpy:215
translate indonesian demo_imagedissolve_transitions_ca316184:

    # e "We can hide things with a 'circleirisin'..."
    e ""

# game/indepth_transitions.rpy:221
translate indonesian demo_imagedissolve_transitions_b8fdf2b6:

    # e "... and show them again with a 'circleirisout'."
    e "... dan menunjukkannya lagi dengan 'circleirisout'." 

# game/indepth_transitions.rpy:227
translate indonesian demo_imagedissolve_transitions_ee427486:

    # e "The 'circlewipe' transitions changes screens using a circular wipe effect."
    e "Transisi 'circlewipe' mengubah layar menggunakan efek sapuan melingkar." 

# game/indepth_transitions.rpy:233
translate indonesian demo_imagedissolve_transitions_6f089276:

    # e "The 'dream' transition does this weird wavy dissolve, and does it relatively slowly."
    e "Transisi 'dream' melakukan dissolve bergelombang yang aneh ini secara relatif lambat." 

# game/indepth_transitions.rpy:239
translate indonesian demo_imagedissolve_transitions_c0b9d74d:

    # e "The 'teleport' transition reveals the new scene one line at a time."
    e "Transisi 'teleport' memunculkan adegan baru baris demi baris." 

# game/indepth_transitions.rpy:246
translate indonesian demo_imagedissolve_transitions_72ba11d4:

    # e "This is the background picture used with the circleirisout transition."
    e "Ini adalah gambar latar belakang yang digunakan dengan transisi circleirisout." 

# game/indepth_transitions.rpy:248
translate indonesian demo_imagedissolve_transitions_fc3b3339:

    # e "When we use an ImageDissolve, the white will dissolve in first, followed by progressively darker colors. Let's try it."
    e "Saat kita menggunakan ImageDissolve, bagian putih akan memudar masuk terlebih dahulu, diikuti oleh warna yang semakin gelap. Mari kita coba." 

# game/indepth_transitions.rpy:255
translate indonesian demo_imagedissolve_transitions_4327dca2:

    # e "If we give ImageDissolve the 'reverse' parameter, black areas will dissolve in first."
    e "Jika kita memberikan parameter 'reverse' pada ImageDissolve, area hitam akan memudar masuk terlebih dahulu." 

# game/indepth_transitions.rpy:260
translate indonesian demo_imagedissolve_transitions_3a401ee7:

    # e "This lets circleirisin and circleirisout use the same image."
    e "Ini memungkinkan circleirisin dan circleirisout menggunakan gambar yang sama." 

# game/indepth_transitions.rpy:267
translate indonesian demo_imagedissolve_transitions_20d9cf6c:

    # e "The teleport transition uses a different image, one that dissolves things in one line at a time."
    e "Transisi teleport menggunakan gambar yang berbeda, yang memudarkan segalanya baris demi baris." 

# game/indepth_transitions.rpy:272
translate indonesian demo_imagedissolve_transitions_906f7800:

    # e "A dissolve only seems to affect parts of the scene that have changed..."
    e ""

# game/indepth_transitions.rpy:277
translate indonesian demo_imagedissolve_transitions_4b557a29:

    # e "... which is how we apply the teleport effect to a single character."
    e "... begitulah cara kita menerapkan efek teleportasi ke satu karakter saja." 

# game/indepth_transitions.rpy:285
translate indonesian demo_cropmove_transitions_1711a91e:

    # e "The CropMove transition class provides a wide range of transition effects. It's not used very much in practice, though."
    e "Kelas transisi CropMove menyediakan berbagai macam efek transisi. Namun, kelas ini tidak terlalu sering digunakan dalam praktiknya." 

# game/indepth_transitions.rpy:290
translate indonesian demo_cropmove_transitions_6d82cfd7:

    # e "I'll stand offscreen, so you can see some of its modes. I'll read out the mode name after each transition."
    e "Saya akan berdiri di luar layar agar kamu bisa melihat beberapa modenya. Saya akan membacakan nama modenya setelah setiap transisi." 

# game/indepth_transitions.rpy:296
translate indonesian demo_cropmove_transitions_4427c78c:

    # e "We first have wiperight..."
    e ""

# game/indepth_transitions.rpy:302
translate indonesian demo_cropmove_transitions_6d1810a1:

    # e "...followed by wipeleft... "
    e ""

# game/indepth_transitions.rpy:308
translate indonesian demo_cropmove_transitions_1dd1c6a1:

    # e "...wipeup..."
    e ""

# game/indepth_transitions.rpy:314
translate indonesian demo_cropmove_transitions_0ea0fa83:

    # e "...and wipedown."
    e "...dan wipedown." 

# game/indepth_transitions.rpy:316
translate indonesian demo_cropmove_transitions_c7cb4c16:

    # e "Next, the slides."
    e "Berikutnya, slide." 

# game/indepth_transitions.rpy:322
translate indonesian demo_cropmove_transitions_462a442f:

    # e "Slideright..."
    e ""

# game/indepth_transitions.rpy:328
translate indonesian demo_cropmove_transitions_f9a2e523:

    # e "...slideleft..."
    e ""

# game/indepth_transitions.rpy:334
translate indonesian demo_cropmove_transitions_20ce3e9c:

    # e "...slideup..."
    e ""

# game/indepth_transitions.rpy:340
translate indonesian demo_cropmove_transitions_9e00a7a6:

    # e "and slidedown."
    e "dan slidedown." 

# game/indepth_transitions.rpy:342
translate indonesian demo_cropmove_transitions_b8a710c1:

    # e "While the slide transitions slide in the new scene, the slideaways slide out the old scene."
    e "Sementara transisi slide menggeser adegan baru masuk, slideaway menggeser adegan lama keluar." 

# game/indepth_transitions.rpy:349
translate indonesian demo_cropmove_transitions_1efb4cd0:

    # e "Slideawayright..."
    e ""

# game/indepth_transitions.rpy:355
translate indonesian demo_cropmove_transitions_bfb5dfd7:

    # e "...slideawayleft..."
    e ""

# game/indepth_transitions.rpy:361
translate indonesian demo_cropmove_transitions_6c1a4a6f:

    # e "...slideawayup..."
    e ""

# game/indepth_transitions.rpy:367
translate indonesian demo_cropmove_transitions_1f994a7b:

    # e "and slideawaydown."
    e "dan slideawaydown." 

# game/indepth_transitions.rpy:369
translate indonesian demo_cropmove_transitions_025ef723:

    # e "We also have a couple of transitions that use a rectangular iris."
    e "Kami juga memiliki beberapa transisi yang menggunakan iris persegi panjang." 

# game/indepth_transitions.rpy:376
translate indonesian demo_cropmove_transitions_d00d505e:

    # e "There's irisout..."
    e ""

# game/indepth_transitions.rpy:383
translate indonesian demo_cropmove_transitions_016a1e0a:

    # e "... and irisin."
    e "... dan irisin." 

# game/indepth_transitions.rpy:387
translate indonesian demo_cropmove_transitions_08d753ed:

    # e "It's enough to make you feel a bit dizzy."
    e "Ini sudah cukup membuat kamu merasa sedikit pusing." 

# game/indepth_transitions.rpy:393
translate indonesian demo_pushmove_transitions_003e506d:

    # e "The PushMove transitions use the new scene to push the old one out. Let's take a look."
    e "Transisi PushMove menggunakan adegan baru untuk mendorong adegan lama keluar. Mari kita lihat." 

# game/indepth_transitions.rpy:401
translate indonesian demo_pushmove_transitions_124f375d:

    # "There's pushright..."
    ""

# game/indepth_transitions.rpy:408
translate indonesian demo_pushmove_transitions_ce380ccb:

    # "...pushleft..."
    ""

# game/indepth_transitions.rpy:416
translate indonesian demo_pushmove_transitions_77629638:

    # "...pushdown..."
    ""

# game/indepth_transitions.rpy:424
translate indonesian demo_pushmove_transitions_b7f33c95:

    # "... and pushup. And that's it the for the PushMove-based transitions."
    e "... dan pushup. Dan itu saja untuk transisi berbasis PushMove." 

# game/indepth_transitions.rpy:434
translate indonesian demo_movetransition_14df0e34:

    # e "The most common MoveTransition is move, which slides around images that have changed position on the screen."
    e "MoveTransition yang paling umum adalah move, yang menggeser gambar-gambar yang telah berubah posisinya di layar." 

# game/indepth_transitions.rpy:442
translate indonesian demo_movetransition_84e40422:

    # e "Just like that."
    e "Tepat seperti itu." 

# game/indepth_transitions.rpy:446
translate indonesian demo_movetransition_098ee9f1:

    # e "There are also the moveout and movein transitions."
    e "Ada juga transisi moveout dan movein." 

# game/indepth_transitions.rpy:448
translate indonesian demo_movetransition_09748f81:

    # e "The moveout transitions (moveoutleft, moveoutright, moveouttop, and moveoutbottom) slide hidden images off the appropriate side of the screen."
    e "Transisi moveout (moveoutleft, moveoutright, moveouttop, dan moveoutbottom) menggeser gambar tersembunyi keluar dari sisi layar yang sesuai." 

# game/indepth_transitions.rpy:450
translate indonesian demo_movetransition_5edf6007:

    # e "The movein transitions (moveinleft, moveinright, moveintop, and moveinbottom) slide in new images."
    e "Transisi movein (moveinleft, moveinright, moveintop, dan moveinbottom) menggeser gambar baru masuk." 

# game/indepth_transitions.rpy:452
translate indonesian demo_movetransition_20946d36:

    # e "Let's see them all in action."
    e "Mari kita lihat semuanya beraksi." 

# game/indepth_transitions.rpy:487
translate indonesian demo_movetransition_569952e3:

    # e "That's it for the moveins and moveouts."
    e "Itu saja untuk movein dan moveout." 

# game/indepth_transitions.rpy:489
translate indonesian demo_movetransition_bbb75540:

    # e "Finally, there are the zoomin and zoomout transitions, which show and hide things using a zoom."
    e "Terakhir, ada transisi zoomin dan zoomout, yang menunjukkan dan menyembunyikan berbagai hal menggunakan zoom." 

# game/indepth_transitions.rpy:499
translate indonesian demo_movetransition_dc5ccd54:

    # e "And that's all there is."
    e "Dan hanya itu saja." 

# game/indepth_transitions.rpy:508
translate indonesian demo_alphadissolve_51613c02:

    # e "The AlphaDissolve transition lets you use one displayable to combine two others. Click, and I'll show you an example."
    e "Transisi AlphaDissolve memungkinkan kamu menggunakan satu displayable untuk menggabungkan dua lainnya. Klik, dan saya akan menunjukkan contohnya kepada kamu." 

# game/indepth_transitions.rpy:518
translate indonesian demo_alphadissolve_7c08cf8b:

    # e "The AlphaDissolve displayable takes a control displayable, usually an ATL transform."
    e "Displayable AlphaDissolve mengambil sebuah kontrol displayable, biasanya berupa transformasi ATL." 

# game/indepth_transitions.rpy:523
translate indonesian demo_alphadissolve_068e3e98:

    # e "To be useful, the control displayable should be partially transparent."
    e "Agar berguna, kontrol displayable tersebut harus transparan sebagian." 

# game/indepth_transitions.rpy:525
translate indonesian demo_alphadissolve_6a1b6203:

    # e "During an AlphaDissolve, the old screen is used to fill the transparent areas of the image, while the new screen fills the opaque areas."
    e "Selama AlphaDissolve, layar lama digunakan untuk mengisi area transparan pada gambar, sedangkan layar baru mengisi area yang buram." 

# game/indepth_transitions.rpy:529
translate indonesian demo_alphadissolve_80a728b6:

    # e "For our spotlight example, the old screen is this all-black image."
    e "Untuk contoh lampu sorot kami, layar lamanya adalah gambar yang sepenuhnya hitam ini." 

# game/indepth_transitions.rpy:534
translate indonesian demo_alphadissolve_ce4380eb:

    # e "The new screen is me just standing here."
    e "Layar barunya adalah saya yang hanya berdiri di sini." 

# game/indepth_transitions.rpy:542
translate indonesian demo_alphadissolve_2e95917b:

    # e "By combining them using AlphaDissolve, we can build a complicated effect out of simpler parts."
    e "Dengan menggabungkannya menggunakan AlphaDissolve, kita dapat membangun efek yang rumit dari bagian-bagian yang lebih sederhana." 

